{"id": "noos014", "name": "Cam_Nora_695_03_03", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Nora'sRoom"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Arc_01", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member I"], "content": "Nora, get ready for your scan... Nora? Where are you~?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>Ichiro.</i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member I"], "content": "Yikes!? Who's calling me!?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>... I'm Nora. Looks like it's a success. I'm behind the shelf.</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "image", "attrs": ["noos1401"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member I"], "content": "Nora!? This machine... did you make this?\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>Yes. The name is \"ROBO_Head\". It's a bit like... a translator, I guess? This way, I'm able to talk.</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member I"], "content": "Wow... So this is your voice?\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>It's a simulation of my voiceprint. I don't know how to talk to begin with, so I have no clue whether this is my voice or not.</i>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member I"], "content": "That's incredible! We're finally able to hear you talk... How did you do that?\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>A.R.C. announced the cyTus technology a while ago. I wrote a program with its protocol. It can directly translate what I want to speak via virtual connection.</i>\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member I"], "content": "It really is incredible. You're truly a child prodigy!\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>There are still some functions I would like to test out. Do you mind helping me out a little bit?</i>\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member I"], "content": "Not a problem!\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>Hmm... Everything's more or less functioning normally. There are some places that can use some minor tweaking... Thank you for helping me out with the tests.</i>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member I"], "content": "This is awesome! We need to tell director ASAP!\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>Wait!</i>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member I"], "content": "Eh?\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>... Still not prepared... about what to tell him...</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member I"], "content": "How come? You're speaking very fluently! On top of that, your speech doesn't sound like a child at all!\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>That's not the problem...\nChildren... How do they talk? I don't know, because all I have around me is you guys.</i>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member I"], "content": "Ah... sorry.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>Why are you apologizing?</i>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member I"], "content": "Umm, nothing. It's just that... when I hear those words coming directly from you, I feel sorry for the kind of life we put you through...\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>I've never had a different life before. Ichiro, you don't have to be sorry.</i>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member I"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Arc_01", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "Ichiro, we asked you to pick up Nora. Why are you taking so long? Everyone's been waiting for you.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member I"], "content": "Ah! Director! Look! Nora is amazing. She made this machine by herself. She is now able to speak!\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>......</i>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "......?\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member I"], "content": "What's wrong? Nora! Show it to director!\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>... H, Hello, I'm Nora...</i>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>... Ummm...</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "... Did you make this with the cyTus technology? Very impressive. You're able to master the programming language I taught you in a very short time.\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>Thank you...</i>\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "Take her to do the scan. We are already having a serious delay.\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member I"], "content": "Ah... Yes sir! I'm sorry!\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>......</i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Nora'sRoom"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Arc_01", "ドアが開く"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員I"], "content": "Noraちゃん、スキャンの準備ができたよ……あれ？Noraちゃん？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>一郎。</i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員I"], "content": "うわ！誰！？誰の声！？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……私、Nora。\n成功したみたい。\n私、棚の後ろにいるよ。</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "image", "attrs": ["noos1401"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員I"], "content": "Noraちゃん！？\nこのロボットは……君が作ったのかい？\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>うん。「ROBO_Head」っていうの。\n翻訳機……みたいな。\nこれで、私、おしゃべりできる。</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員I"], "content": "わぁ……これが君の声？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>私の声紋を使って模倣してるの。\n私はしゃべれないから、この声が本当に私の声かは分からない。</i>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員I"], "content": "すごい！\nやっと君の声が聞けたね……どうやったの？\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>A.R.C.が最近発表したcyTusの技術。\nその協定のプログラムを使ってるの。\n神経ネットワークで、直接、私の話したいことを話せるんだ。</i>\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員I"], "content": "本当にすごいよ！\nNoraちゃんは天才児だね！\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>他にも試したい機能があるんだ。\n付き合ってくれる？</i>\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員I"], "content": "もちろん構わないよ！\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>うん……大体は問題ないかな。\nあとちょっと修正して……付き合ってくれてありがとう。</i>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員I"], "content": "本当に本当にすごいよ！\nチーフに報告しなきゃ！\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>待って！</i>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員I"], "content": "え？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……まだ、何を話すか……考えてないの……</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員I"], "content": "大丈夫だよ！\nすごくスムーズに話せてる！\nそれに子供と会話してるとは思えないくらいだよ！\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>そういう問題じゃなくて……\n子供って……どうやって話すの？\n分からない。\n私の周りには、あなたたちしかいないから。</i>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員I"], "content": "あ……ごめん。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>なんで謝るの？</i>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員I"], "content": "いや、違うんだ。\n君の口からそう言われると……こんな生活をさせてしまってごめんって気持ちになって……\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>私、他の生活なんて知らないから、一郎は謝らなくても大丈夫。</i>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員I"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Arc_01", "ドアが開く"], "content": ""}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "一郎、Noraを連れて来いと言ってからだいぶ時間が経つが、何をしているんだ？\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員I"], "content": "あ！チーフ！聞いてください！\nNoraちゃんすごいんですよ！\nこのロボットを使って話せるようになったんです！\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>………</i>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "………？\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員I"], "content": "ほら、Noraちゃん！どうしたんだい？\nチーフにも見せてあげようよ！\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……こ、こんにちは。Nora……です。</i>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……あの……</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "cyTusの技術を使って作ったのか？すごいな。\n以前教えた文法をもう使えるのか。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>ありがとう……</i>\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "スキャンに行こう。\nもうだいぶ遅れている。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員I"], "content": "あ……はい！すみません！\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>………</i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Nora'sRoom"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Arc_01", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "Nora，準備去做掃描囉……Nora？人呢？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>一郎。</i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "哇！？誰在叫我！？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……我是 Nora，看起來成功了。我在櫃子後面。</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "image", "attrs": ["noos1401"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "Nora！？這台機器……是妳做的嗎？\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>嗯，叫「ROBO_Head」，有點像……翻譯機吧？這樣就能說話了。</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "哇……這是妳的聲音嗎？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>是用我的聲紋模擬的，我本來就不會說話，也不知道到底是不是。</i>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "好厲害！終於聽到妳說話了……妳是怎麼做的？\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>A.R.C. 前陣子發表了 cyTus 技術，我用它的協定寫的程式，它可以透過精神連線直翻我想講的話。</i>\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "真的好厲害，妳真的是天才兒童啊！\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>我還有一些功能想測試一下，可以稍微陪陪我嗎？</i>\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "當然沒問題！\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>嗯……大致上都正常，還有幾個小地方要修……謝謝你陪我測試。</i>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "簡直太棒了！得趕快告訴主任！\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>先等等！</i>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "咦？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……還沒準備好……要跟他說什麼……</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "怎麼會？很流暢啊！而且妳說話完全聽不出是小孩子！\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>不是那個問題……\n小孩子……都是怎麼說話的？我不知道，我身邊只有你們。</i>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "啊……抱歉。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>為什麼道歉？</i>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "呃，不是，因為聽到妳親口這麼說就覺得這樣的生活很對不起妳……\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>我沒有過過別的生活，一郎不用道歉。</i>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Arc_01", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "一郎，叫你來帶 Nora，怎麼那麼久？大家都在等。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "啊！主任！你看！Nora 真的好厲害，做了這台機器，現在她可以說話了！\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……。</i>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "怎麼了？Nora！快讓主任看看啊！\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……你、你好，我是 Nora……</i>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……那個……</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "……用 cyTus 技術做的嗎？很了不起。之前教妳的語法妳一下就學會了。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>謝謝……</i>\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "去做掃描吧，我們已經延遲很久了。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "啊……是！對不起！\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……。</i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Nora'sRoom"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Arc_01", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 I"], "content": "Nora, 스캐닝 준비 좀 부탁할게.... Nora? 거기 없니?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>이치로.</i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 I"], "content": "헉!? 누가 날 부른 거지!?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>...나야, Nora. \n성공한 것 같네. \n난 서랍장 뒤에 있어.</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "image", "attrs": ["noos1401"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 I"], "content": "Nora!? 이 기계는... 네가 만든 거야?\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>응. 「ROBO_Head」라고 부르기로 했어.\n이것은... 통역기 같은 거랄까?\n이렇게면 나도 말을 할 수 있을 테니깐.</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 I"], "content": "와... 네 목소리가 이렇구나...\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>내 성문(聲紋)을 시뮬레이션해서 모방했을 뿐이야. 원래는 말을 할 수 없기 때문에 이게 진짜 내 목소리인지는 확실하지 않아.</i>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 I"], "content": "정말 놀라워! 드디어 네가 말하는 걸 들을 수 있게 되다니... 대체 어떻게 만든 거야?\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>A.R.C.가 앞전에 발표했던 cyTus의 기술. 협정된 프로그래밍 사용으로 정신 네트워크에 접속해서 내가 하고 싶은 말을 할 수 있게 됐어.</i>\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 I"], "content": "정말 대단해! \n정말 넌 신동 중에 신동이라고!\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>아직 테스트해야 할 게 좀 남았는데, 조금 도와줄 수 있어?</i>\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 I"], "content": "물론이지! 말만 하라고!\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>음... 대부분 모두 정상이긴 하지만, 아직 몇 군대는 손을 봐야겠네... 테스트를 도와줘서 고마워.</i>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 I"], "content": "정말 말문이 막히는걸!\n당장 주임님께 말해드려야겠다!\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>잠깐만!</i>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 I"], "content": "응?\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>...아직... 그 사람에게 뭐라고 말해야 할지 준비도 못 했는데...</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 I"], "content": "괜찮을 거야! 지금도 잘만 하는걸! 게다가 지금 어린애와 대화를 나누고 있다는 생각이 전혀 안 들 정도라니깐!\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>그런 문제가 아니야...\n어린아이는... 보통 어떤 식으로 말을 하지? 잘 모르겠어... 내 주위에는 당신들밖에 없어서.</i>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 I"], "content": "아... 미안.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>왜 사과하는 거야?</i>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 I"], "content": "아, 아무것도 아니야. 그냥... 네게 직접 그런 말을 들으니깐... 네게 이런 생활을 시키고 있는 것 같아 미안한 생각이 들어서...\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>나는 다른 방식의 생활을 해본 적이 없어서 잘 몰라. 이치로가 사과할 필요 없어.</i>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 I"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Arc_01", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "이치로, Nora를 데리고 오라니깐 뭘 꾸물거리고 있는 거냐. 다들 기다리고 있다.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 I"], "content": "앗! 주임님! 이것 좀 보세요! Nora는 정말 대단한 아이입니다! 이 기계를 직접 만들었고 이걸로 말까지 할 수 있게 되었어요!\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>......</i>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "......?\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 I"], "content": "왜 그래? Nora! 뭐하고 있어! 빨리 주임님께 보여드리지 않고!\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>...아, 안녕하세요. 저는 Nora...입니다.</i>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": ".....\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>...저...</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "...cyTus의 기술로 만들어 낸 건가? 정말 대단하군. 예전에 가르쳐주었던 문법을 바로 구사해내는구나.\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>감사합니다...</i>\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "서둘러 스캐닝을 시작해. \n이미 시간이 엄청 지연되었으니깐.\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 I"], "content": "아... 네! 죄송합니다!\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>......</i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Nora'sRoom"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Arc_01", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "Nora，準備去做掃描囉……Nora？人呢？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>一郎。</i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "哇！？誰在叫我！？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……我是 Nora，看起來成功了。我在櫃子後面。</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "image", "attrs": ["noos1401"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "Nora！？這台機器……是妳做的嗎？\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>嗯，叫「ROBO_Head」，有點像……翻譯機吧？這樣就能說話了。</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "哇……這是妳的聲音嗎？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>是用我的聲紋模擬的，我本來就不會說話，也不知道到底是不是。</i>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "好厲害！終於聽到妳說話了……妳是怎麼做的？\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>A.R.C. 前陣子發表了 cyTus 技術，我用它的協定寫的程式，它可以透過精神連線直翻我想講的話。</i>\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "真的好厲害，妳真的是天才兒童啊！\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>我還有一些功能想測試一下，可以稍微陪陪我嗎？</i>\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "當然沒問題！\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>嗯……大致上都正常，還有幾個小地方要修……謝謝你陪我測試。</i>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "簡直太棒了！得趕快告訴主任！\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>先等等！</i>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "咦？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……還沒準備好……要跟他說什麼……</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "怎麼會？很流暢啊！而且妳說話完全聽不出是小孩子！\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>不是那個問題……\n小孩子……都是怎麼說話的？我不知道，我身邊只有你們。</i>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "啊……抱歉。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>為什麼道歉？</i>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "呃，不是，因為聽到妳親口這麼說就覺得這樣的生活很對不起妳……\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>我沒有過過別的生活，一郎不用道歉。</i>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Arc_01", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "一郎，叫你來帶 Nora，怎麼那麼久？大家都在等。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "啊！主任！你看！Nora 真的好厲害，做了這台機器，現在她可以說話了！\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……。</i>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "怎麼了？Nora！快讓主任看看啊！\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……你、你好，我是 Nora……</i>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……那個……</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "……用 cyTus 技術做的嗎？很了不起。之前教妳的語法妳一下就學會了。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>謝謝……</i>\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "去做掃描吧，我們已經延遲很久了。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "啊……是！對不起！\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……。</i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Nora'sRoom"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Arc_01", "开门"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["组员 I"], "content": "Nora，准备去做扫描啰……Nora？人呢？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>一郎。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["组员 I"], "content": "哇！ ？谁在叫我！ ？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……我是 Nora，看起来成功了。我在柜子后面。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "image", "attrs": ["noos1401"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["组员 I"], "content": "Nora！ ？这台机器……是妳做的吗？\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>嗯，叫「ROBO_Head」，有点像……翻译机吧？这样就能说话了。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["组员 I"], "content": "哇……这是妳的声音吗？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>是用我的声纹模拟的，我本来就不会说话，也不知道到底是不是。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["组员 I"], "content": "好厉害！终于听到妳說话了……妳是怎么做的？\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>A.R.C. 前阵子发表了 cyTus 技术，我用它的协定写的程式，它可以透过精神连线直翻我想讲的话。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["组员 I"], "content": "真的好厉害，妳真的是天才儿童啊！\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>我还有一些功能想测试一下，可以稍微陪陪我吗？ </i>\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["组员 I"], "content": "当然没问题！\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快转»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>嗯……大致上都正常，还有几个小地方要修……谢谢你陪我测试。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["组员 I"], "content": "简直太棒了！得赶快告诉主任！\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>先等等！ </i>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["组员 I"], "content": "咦？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……还没准备好……要跟他说什么……</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["组员 I"], "content": "怎么会？很流畅啊！而且妳說话完全听不出是小孩子！\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>不是那个问题……\n小孩子……都是怎么说话的？我不知道，我身边只有你们。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["组员 I"], "content": "啊……抱歉。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>为什么道歉？ </i>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["组员 I"], "content": "呃，不是，因为听到妳亲口这么说就觉得这样的生活很对不起妳……\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>我没有过过别的生活，一郎不用道歉。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["组员 I"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Arc_01", "开门"], "content": ""}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "一郎，叫你来带 Nora，怎么那么久？大家都在等。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["组员 I"], "content": "啊！主任！你看！ Nora 真的好厉害，做了这台机器，现在她可以说话了！\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["组员 I"], "content": "怎么了？ Nora！快让主任看看啊！\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……你、你好，我是 Nora……</i>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……那个……</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "……用 cyTus 技术做的吗？很了不起。之前教妳的语法妳一下就学会了。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>谢谢……</i>\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": 